```plantuml
@startuml lowtalkers_escape-reality

actor User
participant "React Client" as ReactClient
participant "Node.js Server" as Server
participant "MariaDB" as Database
participant "AWS S3" as S3
participant "Wikipedia API" as WikipediaAPI

User -> ReactClient: Login
ReactClient -> Server: POST /api/login
Server -> Database: Validate User Credentials
Database -> Server: User Credentials Validated
Server -> ReactClient: Authentication Token

User -> ReactClient: Explore Scenes
ReactClient -> Server: GET /api/scenes
Server -> Database: Fetch Scene Data
Database -> Server: Scene Data
Server -> ReactClient: Scene Data

User -> ReactClient: Upload Image
ReactClient -> S3: Upload Image
S3 -> ReactClient: Image URL
ReactClient -> Server: POST /api/images
Server -> Database: Store Image Metadata
Database -> Server: Acknowledgement
Server -> ReactClient: Image Upload Success

User -> ReactClient: Comment on Image
ReactClient -> Server: POST /api/comments
Server -> Database: Store Comment
Database -> Server: Acknowledgement
Server -> ReactClient: Comment Success

User -> ReactClient: Like Image
ReactClient -> Server: POST /api/likes
Server -> Database: Update Like Count
Database -> Server: Acknowledgement
Server -> ReactClient: Like Success

User -> ReactClient: Bookmark Article
ReactClient -> WikipediaAPI: Fetch Article
WikipediaAPI -> ReactClient: Article Content
ReactClient -> Server: POST /api/bookmarks
Server -> Database: Store Bookmark
Database -> Server: Acknowledgement
Server -> ReactClient: Bookmark Success

@enduml
```